description: Moves phone numbers into the Deletion queue. Phone numbers must be disassociated from any users or Amazon Chime Voice Connectors before they can be deleted. Phone numbers remain in the Deletion queue for 7 days before they are deleted permanently.

nested_items.name: PhoneNumberErrors
nested_items.description: If the action fails for one or more of the phone numbers in the request, a list of the phone numbers is returned, along with error codes and error messages.

nested_items.name: PhoneNumberId
nested_items.description: The phone number ID for which the action failed.
